<p>The idea stuck and we began our work. I handled the facial detection components. I taught myself how the OpenCV library worked and created a framework to manage our project. Furthermore, I began learning
about CMake to simplify our build process (that came in handy) and practiced Git with our shared GitHub repo.</p>

<p>Before we disassemble the project for parts, IтАЩm going to try my hand at training the facial detection algorithm on my own face. IтАЩve always been fascinated by computer vision and I canтАЩt a more
